#%PAM-1.0
# Minimal proot-friendly stack. Arch's system-login/system-auth pull in
# pam_systemd_home, pam_faillock, pam_shells, pam_systemd - all of which throw
# PAM_SYSTEM_ERR under proot (no systemd/dbus). shadow is 644-readable here, so
# plain pam_unix authenticates directly.
auth       required   pam_unix.so
account    required   pam_unix.so
password   required   pam_unix.so
session    required   pam_unix.so
